{"title": "How to Send Investigation Results via email?", "body": "Follow these steps on how to send Investigation Results using email on Demand:\nOpen Patient Record\nClick Investigation and Click Results\nLocate the Results you want to send then Tick the Box\nClick More then Select Print.\nUnder the \"Destination\" section, select \"Save as PDF\" to download the results and Click Save\n\n\nGo back to the Patient Record \nClick Clinical Tab and Select Correspondence OUT\nClick Import and fill in all required fields.\nThe required fields are as follows: Set the 'Status' to 'Final,' select 'Any Subject and Details', choose the 'Results' category, and upload the Results files.\n\nClick Save\nFor additional steps in sending Results to patients or contacts using email on demand, please see this article. How to Send an Email to Contacts or Patient.\n  What is Email on Demand?\n   "}